snippet.title: Minecraft Marketplace Summer Celebration
snippet.description:
Start the summer off with a Minecraft Marketplace Summer Celebration! Between June 29 - July 12 you’ll find lots of items on sale in Minecraft Marketplace, along with a daily free Character Creator item and two free maps made by Rasa Studios and Oreville Studios! Read more here: https://minecraft.net/article/the-marketplace-summer-celebration-sale-here

AUDIO DESCRIPTION version is here: https://youtu.be/mlZrthu6Utw
